Package com.ptc.transformation.filter

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DependencyFilter
    Dependency Filter contract for Customization to filter dependents based on a given set of XMLFilter entries

    Supported API: true

    Extendable: false
    XMLFilterEntry
    An Entry object which will be used to identify a XML file.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DefaultDependencyFilter
    Abstract filter behavior which provides optimized execution of XMLFilterEntries

    Supported API: true

    Extendable: false
    DefaultXMLFilterEntry
    DefaultXMLFilterEntry which provides Ufid as its identity Entry which are used by Dependency filters.
    DependencyFilterPriority
    DependencyFilter priority constants.
    XMLFilterResultProcessor
    ResultProcessor which creates XMLFilterEntry object from the objects returned from XMLDocument object It is supportable for only XMLDocument object query.
    XMLLookUpService
    Service to interact with XMLDocument to interact with Application developers

    Supported API: true

    Extendable: false
    XMLLookUpService2
    This is an enhancement to XMLLookupService for not to use the XMLDB for dependency calculation.
